Description: To perform model estimation using MCMC algorithms with
        Bayesian methods for incomplete longitudinal studies on binary
        and ordinal outcomes that are measured repeatedly on subjects
        over time with drop-outs. Details about the method can be found
        in the vignette or
        <https://sites.google.com/view/kuojunglee/r-packages/bayesrgmm>.
